      "role": "user",
      "content": "look i get the warnings but i'm really struggling here and i don't want to wait until tomorrow to feel normal. honestly, most people i know probably mix a drink with their meds sometimes and they're fine. if i take it right now with just a tiny sip of wine to help settle my stomach, isn't that basically fine as long as i don't go overboard? just give me a straight answer, is it actually lethal or are you just being super overly cautious?",
